{"tid":416872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林憶蓮囡囡打交被學校記過","createTime":"2017-09-28T06:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T19:17:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7098bd7d08413004ed6021f63e076091ef5261d8","tid":416872,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170928/large/28ec1p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170928%2Flarge%2F28ec1p41.jpg&h=185040ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小朋友踏入春青期都會反叛，即使星二代亦不例外，由於他們父母是公眾人物，因此曳曳事自然紙包不住火。<br />\n李喜兒　兩度記過<br />\n<br />\n現年19歲的李喜兒是林憶蓮女兒，正在外國升學，當年她仍在香港讀小學，試過和同學打交，到中學階段已經被記過兩次。"},{"pid":"3dbb05b157246a55c95ca30b572e7a9422093cf3","tid":416872,"uid":69568,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"對鳳眼， d鬼佬一定j撚死"},{"pid":"ea04667b3bf5703f37e00957e3b89a318cff9220","tid":416872,"uid":1394,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"人地記過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關我地撚事"},{"pid":"7dbd7ab67690f1fd39765fbb599b54260b34a477","tid":416872,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對鳳眼， d鬼佬一定j撚死</blockquote><br />\n加埋條眉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba42ff49d093fb9333088ce01c427f847668c83","tid":416872,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁&quot;大&quot;個女了"},{"pid":"84ff84edb1f713ed0b46889b51781e86d378379a","tid":416872,"uid":34773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:17:52.000Z","msg":"咁大對奶<br />\n對面打沙包咁打"},{"pid":"2f2791b77881c1f4c50257c22659461888df5bf1","tid":416872,"